OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fwith late sunshine then clear spells
OL,7,Falways more prolonged towards the
OL,8,Fsouthern end of the Great Glen. North
OL,9,Fto northeast winds occasionally fresh
OL,10,Facross the Hebrides.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAnother generally fair days
OL,13,Fweather in prospect with most dry with
OL,14,Fperiods of sunshine widespread through
OL,15,Fthe morning, before turning hazy from
OL,16,Fthe west during the afternoon. Winds
OL,17,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
